{"tid":2205781,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"——九巴有傻仔唔見銀包，自己入嚟攞啦——","createTime":"2020-09-17T05:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T09:06:55.000Z","uid":15849,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bd9e6fa622f9b97111dc58ab748c155eee9a6d45","tid":2205781,"uid":15849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:14:42.000Z","msg":"啱喺深水埗上咗架九巴一坐低見到有個銀包<br />\n<br />\ndetails唔講咁多，傻仔自己add我tg: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/stomachacheking\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstomachacheking&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=5b65ffda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stomachacheking</a><br />\n<br />\n要講得返入面啲嘢<br />\n<br />\n我唔撚想去狗屋，又驚站頭有人白撞，所以唔講咩線，如果今晚都冇人認領我唯有聽日就交去呢條線嘅總站。有其他好方法歡迎留言提供。<br />\n<br />\n入面都多證件，麻煩大家幫手推下俾物主見到"},{"pid":"3ff3b875a3c3a1d81193dee225e0f75a956511f3","tid":2205781,"uid":15849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:14:54.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723f4ee01eb7e35facd6aedb47f9b5b86e3beca4","tid":2205781,"uid":15849,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:15:10.000Z","msg":"唔見銀包好撚慘"},{"pid":"caf4ec7642c17f9526e07d06259fb0612a78ad60","tid":2205781,"uid":15849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:15:48.000Z","msg":"試過唔見銀包跑晒港九新界屯門灣仔"},{"pid":"20dc38ad1231ed5e1b3ebe2b20a7bbae76ce1137","tid":2205781,"uid":15849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:16:06.000Z","msg":"I know that feel"},{"pid":"2bf058349231a2af22eb0db299821d418081848e","tid":2205781,"uid":293579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫推"},{"pid":"b7b3edea8e010290af445b89955351192c0425d9","tid":2205781,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:1